    <briefdescription>
<para>Constrains types that provide a noexcept-less `clear()` method returning void. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Used by IsCommandBuffer to verify that a concrete command buffer supports discarding all queued commands without executing them.</para>
